tagline: GNOME.Asia Event Site of 2009 with the FOSSASIA Community in Vietnam
body:
### Welcome to 2009.fossasia.org

Please help us to get the [2009 event website of the GNOME.Asia Summit](https://web.archive.org/web/20130827220300/http://2009.gnome.asia/), that we organized back online.
All details are in the issue [https://github.com/fossasia/labs.fossasia.org/issues/139](https://github.com/fossasia/labs.fossasia.org/issues/139)
